node.text:
Our next installment of G-Suite Conversations…the Women Grow podcast. 

Keep Inviting Different People to the Table: Emily Paxhia 

Gia welcomes Emily Paxhia, Co-Founder and Managing Partner of Cannabis Investment Firm @poseidon.investments 

Emily has helped to shape many pitches, presentations, and has reviewed thousands of investment questions. She talks with us about applying her education in psychology to business, and why there is nothing like being in the room and learning to speak up confidently with your own opinion. Emily shares why she decided to give cannabis a chance as an early investor in 2012 and start Poseidon with her brother Morgan, along with the important things we should know developing in the present and future within the cannabis investment space. Emily gives an inside look at how smaller companies can approach potential investors, and how she feels megastores will impact the industry. 

#Gsuiteconversations #womengrow #womenincannabis

I found healing properties in honey that benefit me and my children. And now I’m building a hemp and a honey farm. I’ve even got hives on my roof!
